column2: SELECT TOP # s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, p.run, p.rerun, p.camCol, p.field, p.obj, cast (str (p.ra, #, #) as float) as ra, cast (str (p.[dec], #, #) as float) as dec, p.r FROM ..SpecObj as s JOIN ..Galaxy AS p ON s.bestObjID = p.objID JOIN dbo.fGetObjFromRect (#, #, #, #) AS b ON s.bestobjid = b.objID
